To facilitate comparison of Osborn's diagnoses I have compiled in tabular form most of the characters that Osborn used to define the Wind River species of 

Eotitanops

for which there was dental material available (

Table 
1

). All of the characters that Osborn used in the diagnosis of more than one species are included in the table, but I have omitted some of the characters that Osborn used in the diagnosis of only a single species.
